== {rbtr_director} Operations

[[rbtgo_trigger_build]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_trigger_build}

ELIMINATED (₣Av): Trigger dispatch replaced by direct `builds.create` API submission.
Build context delivered via pouch (FROM SCRATCH OCI image in GAR).
Hallmark minted locally by the Director before submission.

// include::RBSTB-trigger_build.adoc[]

NOTE: For multi-platform build authentication challenges and research findings, see link:RBWMBX-BuildxMultiPlatformAuth.adoc[RBWMBX: Buildx Multi-Platform Authentication Memo].

[[rbtgo_image_delete]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_image_delete}

Jettisons
{rbtgi_image}
artifacts
({rbtgog_image}).

include::RBSIJ-image_jettison.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_image_retrieve]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_image_retrieve}

Wrests
{rbtgi_image}
artifacts
({rbtgog_image}).

include::RBSIW-image_wrest.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_image_rekon]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_image_rekon}

Lists all tags for a
{rbtga_vessel}
package in
{rbtgi_repository}
({rbtgog_image}).

include::RBSIR-image_rekon.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_ark_abjure]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_ark_abjure}

Formally renounces an
{rbtga_ark}
from the repository
({rbtgog_ark}),
removing its image, about, and vouch artifacts as a coherent unit.

include::RBSAA-ark_abjure.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_ark_ordain]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_ark_ordain}

Ordains a hallmark from a vessel — the master ceremony dispatch operation.
Detects vessel mode (conjure, bind, or graft) and delegates to the appropriate
{rbtga_ark}
creation path, then chains metadata and vouch pipeline stages.

[[rbtgo_ark_conjure]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_ark_conjure}

Conjures an
{rbtga_ark_image}
by building a container image
({rbtgog_ark})
from a vessel specification.
Build context delivered via pouch (FROM SCRATCH OCI image in GAR), submitted via `builds.create` API. The combined job produces both `-image` and `-about` (about steps embedded via stitch). Vouch is a separate Cloud Build job using DSSE envelope signature verification.

include::RBSAC-ark_conjure.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_ark_enshrine]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_ark_enshrine}

Enshrines upstream base images into
{gar_service}
({rbtgog_ark}),
